## 🛠️ DÉPENDANCES EXTERNES

### JavaScript Libraries
```html
<!-- Dans admin/controller/event/header.php, ajouter au <head> -->

<!-- Screenshot capture -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"></script>

<!-- Charts (si analytics activé) -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.0/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>

<!-- Session replay (optionnel - Phase 3) -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/rrweb@latest/dist/rrweb.min.js"></script>
```

### PHP Requirements
- OpenCart 4.x
- PHP 7.4+
- cURL extension (pour webhooks)
- GD ou Imagick (pour manipulation screenshots si nécessaire)

